Croatia May Join European Union on July 1, 2013, Welt Reports

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-05-22T12:49:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-22/croatia-may-join-european-union-on-july-1-2013-welt-reports.html
The European Commission wants  Croatia 
to join the  European Union  on July 1, 2013,  Welt am Sonntag
reported , citing unidentified diplomats familiar with
negotiations.  The Commission is using that date for its budget planning,
the German newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 